questions.query: What features or use cases does your dApp/App present? How is it differentiated?
questions.explanation:
Yoki Finance is a Web3 subscription payment gateway.

We're the payment layer for the new subscription economy.

Thousands of subscription-based businesses/communities in Web3 charge customers with single payments instead of subscriptions and lose retention and time. We help automate the process reducing the churn rate and saving time.

Others are using Web2 subscription gateways (eg Stripe) which are prone to censorship and fund freezing.

Yoki Finance offers a solution which is:
- Permissionless
- Censorship-resistant
- Non-custodial
- Multichain
- Composable

questions.query: What are your plans for further development, and how will the grant funds be used to achieve these goals?
questions.explanation:
The project is independent and has not received VC funding. The grant will be used to fund the development process and increase our runway!

We're working towards launching a self-service platform for the merchants
